ress.com/2013/11/headshot2.jpg?w=49&#038;h=52&#038;crop=1" alt="Andrew Sharp" /></a><div class="bd"><h3 class="subheading delta"><a name="&lpos=grantlandSiteNav&lid=Contributors_Contributor16" href="http://grantland.com/contributors/andrew-sharp/">Andrew Sharp</a></h3></div></li></ul></div></div><a href="http://grantland.com/contributors/" name="&lpos=grantlandSiteNav&lid=Contributors" class="see-all"><em>See</em> All Contributors</a></div>
